{"parse":{"title":"Bernard Desclot","pageid":12540301,"revid":841605744,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox vcard\" style=\"width:22em\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\"><span class=\"fn\">Bernard Desclot</span></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/File:BernatDesclot.jpg\" class=\"image\" title=\"The Bernard Desclot monument which was built in 1888 and was destroyed in 1937. The photograph was taken in 1910\"><img alt=\"The Bernard Desclot monument which was built in 1888 and was destroyed in 1937. The photograph was taken in 1910\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/55/BernatDesclot.jpg/220px-BernatDesclot.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"424\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/55/BernatDesclot.jpg 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"311\" data-file-height=\"599\" /></a><div>The Bernard Desclot monument which was built in 1888 and was destroyed in 1937. The photograph was taken in 1910</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-top:0.225em;line-height:1.1em;padding-right:0.65em;\">Born</th><td style=\"line-height:1.4em;\">\n1288</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-top:0.225em;line-height:1.1em;padding-right:0.65em;\">Language</th><td style=\"line-height:1.4em;\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/Catalan_language\" title=\"Catalan language\">Catalan language</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-top:0.225em;line-height:1.1em;padding-right:0.65em;\">Nationality</th><td class=\"category\" style=\"line-height:1.4em;\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/Catalans\" title=\"Catalans\">Catalan</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-top:0.225em;line-height:1.1em;padding-right:0.65em;\">Genre</th><td class=\"category\" style=\"line-height:1.4em;\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/Chroniclers\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Chroniclers\">Chronicler</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Bernard Desclot</b> (in <a href=\"/wiki/Catalan_language\" title=\"Catalan language\">Catalan</a>: Bernat Desclot) was a <a href=\"/wiki/Catalonia\" title=\"Catalonia\">Catalan</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Chronicle\" title=\"Chronicle\">chronicler</a> whose work covering the brief reign of <a href=\"/wiki/Peter_III_of_Aragon\" title=\"Peter III of Aragon\">Peter III of Aragon</a> (1276\u201385) forms one of the four <i>Catalan Grand Chronicles</i>  through which the modern historian views thirteenth- and fourteenth century military and political matters in the  <a href=\"/wiki/Kingdom_of_Aragon\" title=\"Kingdom of Aragon\">Kingdom of Aragon</a> and the <a href=\"/wiki/Principality_of_Catalonia\" title=\"Principality of Catalonia\">Principality of Catalonia</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> including the \"<a href=\"/wiki/Aragonese_Crusade\" title=\"Aragonese Crusade\">Aragonese Crusade</a>\". Desclot's <i>Chronicle</i> begins in the eleventh century but gains especial interest when he comes to describe events current within living memory. Bernard's literary model was <a href=\"/wiki/Romance_(heroic_literature)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Romance (heroic literature)\">Romance</a>, and his account is spiced with dramatic monologues of the central characters and thrilling episodes, such as the escape of Peter's brother, <a href=\"/wiki/James_II_of_Majorca\" title=\"James II of Majorca\">James II of Majorca</a>, from the fortress of <a href=\"/wiki/Perpignan\" title=\"Perpignan\">Perpignan</a>, through the castle's drains.\n</p><p>Nothing of Bernard himself is known save what little can be gleaned through his <i>Chronicle</i>.\n</p><p>F.L. Critchlow provided an English translation of the section covering the reign of Peter III in <i>Chronicle of the Reign of King Peter III of Aragon, 1276-85</i> (Princeton University Press) 1928.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Galery\">Galery</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Bernard_Desclot&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Galery\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:15px auto;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Cr%C3%B2nica-bernat-desclot-ms-1-BC-f8r.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Cr\u00f2nica-bernat-desclot-ms-1-BC-f8r.jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/ba/Cr%C3%B2nica-bernat-desclot-ms-1-BC-f8r.jpg/90px-Cr%C3%B2nica-bernat-desclot-ms-1-BC-f8r.jpg\" width=\"90\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/ba/Cr%C3%B2nica-bernat-desclot-ms-1-BC-f8r.jpg/136px-Cr%C3%B2nica-bernat-desclot-ms-1-BC-f8r.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/ba/Cr%C3%B2nica-bernat-desclot-ms-1-BC-f8r.jpg/181px-Cr%C3%B2nica-bernat-desclot-ms-1-BC-f8r.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"748\" data-file-height=\"992\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:15px auto;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Cr%C3%B2nica-desclot-ms-647-BNE.f33r.aragonesos-i-catalans_copy.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Cr\u00f2nica-desclot-ms-647-BNE.f33r.aragonesos-i-catalans copy.jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9b/Cr%C3%B2nica-desclot-ms-647-BNE.f33r.aragonesos-i-catalans_copy.jpg/85px-Cr%C3%B2nica-desclot-ms-647-BNE.f33r.aragonesos-i-catalans_copy.jpg\" width=\"85\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9b/Cr%C3%B2nica-desclot-ms-647-BNE.f33r.aragonesos-i-catalans_copy.jpg/127px-Cr%C3%B2nica-desclot-ms-647-BNE.f33r.aragonesos-i-catalans_copy.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/com